wiki_section_text: 

intro: The 2009 season is Universitario de Deportes' 81st season in the Peruvian Primera División and 44th in the Campeonato Descentralizado. This article shows player statistics and all matches (official and friendly) that the club played during the 2009 season. The season's biggest highlight was the signing of Nolberto Solano.
